    java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.reflect.Constructor<FactorFunction>>

    public class FactorFunctionRegistry
extends ConstructorRegistry<FactorFunction>
    Registry of known FactorFunction implementations.

    Supports lookup and instantiation of factor functions by class name. This is primarily for use in supporting dynamic language API's (e.g. MATLAB).
